data.description: Welcome home!! This beautiful 3bed 2.5 bath house is only 5 years old and well taken care of. Spacious living space opens up to the dining area. All black kitchen appliances and granite counter tops. Upstairs offers a loft that can be used as a kids play area or a second living space. The master bedroom presents a nook area to enjoy your sunrise morning coffee. Double vanity in the master bath with a tub/shower combo and walk in closet. A great backyard for entertaining with an oversize covered back patio. Location, location, location!! Within walking distance to restaurants in Freiheit Village. Short drive to shopping and grocery store. Major hospital nearby with a walking trail around the campus. Future development, Solms Landing behind the property, will bring more shopping and dining options.
